  "page": 200,
  "spans": [
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0002",
      "text": " 181",
      "bbox": [
        518.28,
        723.59,
        537.71,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0003",
      "text": "7.1.2.4  PA required by responder, supported by originator",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        373.11,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0004",
      "text": "If the Responder requires PAs, the Responder is expected to communicate only when a valid Re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        82.97,
        539.95,
        94.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0005",
      "text": "sponder PA is included in the initial Association_Header.  The Responder provides a final",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        94.97,
        539.89,
        106.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0006",
      "text": "Association_Header and provides other Association_Headers as required.  The PA establishes a",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        106.97,
        539.95,
        118.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0007",
      "text": "routing to a particular Responder process.  There is no relationship between PAs identified through",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        118.97,
        539.9,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0008",
      "text": "one Nx_Port of a host system and another Nx_Port from the same host.  The PA may additionally be",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        130.97,
        539.93,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0009",
      "text": "used by the FC-4 in a FC-4 dependent manner.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        142.96,
        305.93,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0010",
      "text": "The PRLI request pages have valid Responder PA values and invalid Originator PA values.  The Re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        166.96,
        539.96,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0011",
      "text": "sponder PA values may be obtained through an informative PRLI operation or by other methods not",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        178.96,
        539.97,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0012",
      "text": "specified.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.96,
        138.14,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0013",
      "text": "The PRLI and PRLO may allow control over the enabling and disabling the access of each Respond-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.96,
        540.03,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0014",
      "text": "er Process to the Originating Nx_Port.  Communication with image pairs that have not been estab-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        226.96,
        540.09,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0015",
      "text": "lished is not allowed, even if both PAs exist and have the proper requirements and capabilities.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        238.96,
        514.88,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0016",
      "text": "7.1.2.5  PA required by originator and responder",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        262.96,
        324.84,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0017",
      "text": "Communication should only take place between an Originator and a Responder when valid PAs are",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        286.96,
        540.04,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0018",
      "text": "specified.  The PA may additionally be used by the FC-4 in a FC-4 dependent manner.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        298.96,
        478.16,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0019",
      "text": "The PRLI request pages shall have valid Originator and Responder PA values defined and shall have",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        322.96,
        539.96,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0020",
      "text": "the Establish Image Pair bit set to one in order to create image pairs in an binding manner.  The Re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        334.96,
        540.03,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0021",
      "text": "sponder PA values may be obtained through an informative PRLI operation or by other methods not",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        346.96,
        539.97,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0022",
      "text": "specified.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        358.96,
        138.14,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0023",
      "text": "PRLI and PRLO pages with complete Originator PA and Responder PA information enable or disable",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        382.96,
        539.99,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0024",
      "text": "communication between the specified image pair.  PRLI pages with incomplete Originator PA and",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        394.96,
        539.81,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0025",
      "text": "Responder PA information are invalid.  Communication with image pairs that have not been estab-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        406.96,
        540.13,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0026",
      "text": "lished is not allowed, even if both PAs exist and have the proper requirements and capabilities.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        418.96,
        514.88,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0027",
      "text": "7.1.3",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        442.96,
        118.22,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0028",
      "text": "Mode of operation",
      "bbox": [
        128.22,
        442.96,
        214.83,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0029",
      "text": "7.1.3.1  Informative mode",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        466.96,
        215.4,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0030",
      "text": "Service Parameter information is exchanged enabling subsequent negotiation for image pair estab-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        490.96,
        539.94,
        502.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0031",
      "text": "lishment.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        135.98,
        514.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0032",
      "text": "7.1.3.2  Binding mode",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        526.96,
        198.75,
        538.07
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0033",
      "text": "Information is exchanged that explicitly establishes a relationship between processes in the commu-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        540.02,
        562.07
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0034",
      "text": "nicating Nx_Ports.  The relationship does not allow any communication types or paths other than",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        562.96,
        539.95,
        574.07
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0035",
      "text": "those established by the PRLI.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        574.96,
        231.51,
        586.07
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0036",
      "text": "The use of a Binding PRLI page requires that the Originator have precise and detailed knowledge of",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        598.96,
        540.06,
        610.07
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0037",
      "text": "the PAs and capabilities available in the Responder.  That information may be obtained from Directo-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        610.96,
        539.98,
        622.07
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0038",
      "text": "ry Services, implicitly from configuration information obtained outside the scope of FC, or by perform-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        622.96,
        540.03,
        634.07
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0039",
      "text": "ing an Informative PRLI.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        634.96,
        203.19,
        646.07
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0040",
      "text": "Binding or Informative mode is determined by the setting of the Establish Image Pair bit in the PRLI",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        659.02,
        540.07,
        670.13
      ],
      "block_index": 17,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p200_s0041",
      "text": "request page.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        671.02,
        157.07,
        682.13
      ],
      "block_index": 17,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    }
  ],
  "asset_ids": []
}